    <!-- Chaos Undivided -->

    <FactionDef ParentName="FactionBase">
        <defName>BEWH_ChaosUndivided</defName>
        <label>Chaos Undivided</label>
        <description>"Mortals kneel; the Gods reward ambition."
A cabal of heretics, renegades, and mutants, the Chaos Undivided faction seeks to drown RimWorld in anarchy and dark glory. Cultist Zealots charge into battle with chainswords, detonating in warpfire upon death, while Traitor Guardsmen pepper colonies with corrupted plasma guns. Dark Acolytes summon Nurglings or hurl bolts of Change, and Possessed Berserkers smash through walls with daemon-fueled strength. Their leaders—Sorcerer Lords and Havoc Marines—wield psychic devastation and rotary cannons, epitomizing the fusion of mortal ambition and daemonic pact. Infiltrators spread "Warp Rot" through sabotage, while Dark Apostles rally hordes with chants to the Ruinous Powers. Though weaker individually than daemons, they swarm in numbers, mutate mid-combat, and occasionally summon Greater Daemons to tip the scales. Align with them at your peril: their gifts come with creeping mutations, and their loyalty lasts only until the next betrayal.</description>
