    <!-- Chaos Daemons Hidden Faction -->

    <FactionDef ParentName="FactionBase">
        <defName>BEWH_ChaosFactionHidden</defName>
        <label>Chaos Daemons</label>
        <description>"The Neverborn march. Reality unravels."
Born from the roiling Warp, the Chaos Daemons are manifestations of the Dark Gods’ will, unbound by mortal flesh or sanity. Khorne’s Bloodletters carve through defenses with hellforged blades, while Nurgle’s Plaguebearers spew pestilence that withers crops and lungs alike. Tzeentch’s Pink Horrors rain warpfire and splinter into shrieking Blue Horrors upon death, and Slaanesh’s Daemonettes dart through combat with euphoric cruelty. Rare but catastrophic, these daemons arrive via warp rifts or sacrificial rituals, their mere presence warping the land with corruption. Beware the Soul Grinder, a biomechanical titan that bombards colonies with daemonic artillery, or the Daemon Prince, an ascended warlord whose roar shatters minds. Immune to pain and fear, they are countered only by fire, faith, or overwhelming firepower. The longer they linger, the higher the risk of "Warp Instability"—random explosions, psychic madness, or spontaneous daemonic reinforcements.</description>
